    slider-controlled Y-coordinate
  image_positioning: Background image fills complete lower half with dynamic Y-coordinate
    - higher slider values result in smaller Y-coordinate (image starts higher up),
    full width coverage, NO rounded corners or frames around the image
  layout_behavior: Split layout with standort top-left, headline under standort, benefits
    DIRECTLY UNDER headline (vertical stack), stellentitel and CTA positioned bottom-left
    IN FRONT OF the background image with larger spacing from benefits, background
    image fills complete lower half with dynamic Y-coordinate based on slider (higher
    slider = smaller Y-coordinate = more image area)
