  split_structure: Upper half contains text elements (standort, headline, benefits
    in vertical stack), lower half contains stellentitel, CTA IN FRONT OF the background
    image and background image with dynamic Y-coordinate
  style_guidelines: Modern, clean design with professional typography, visible white
    containers with shadows, no borders or outlines, corporate color scheme, split
    layout
  text_positioning: Text elements in visible white containers with rounded corners,
    subtle shadows, no borders - standort top-left, headline under standort, benefits
    DIRECTLY UNDER headline (vertical stack), stellentitel and CTA positioned bottom-left
    IN FRONT OF the background image with larger spacing
  visual_structure: Split composition with text elements in upper half, background
    image in lower half, dynamic split line based on slider
